{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Historical Fashion Dress up is a game that lets you explore fashion in Europe, and especially Christiania (today Oslo). The garments are inspired by museum collections and contemporary fashion plates. </h2><br>The first fashion pack is dedicated to early 1820s fashion. You step into the shoes of Tailor Hoff or Seamstress Madam Lind, and create your own Mr. Darcy or Miss Bennet, or perhaps your dream attire. It\u2019s all up to you!<br><br>\ud83d\udcd6 <strong>Historical Accuracy</strong><br>Every garment is researched and recreated, offering an authentic experience of the era's style. You can also read more about the fashion in our info menu.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/Dress_02.gif?t=1725550327\" /><br><br>\u270d\ufe0f<strong>Character Customization</strong><br>Not just limited to clothing, customizing the appearance of your characters. Experiment with facial features, hairstyles, accessories, and more to bring your character to life.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/Character_02.gif?t=1725550327\" /><br><br>\ud83d\udcf7<strong>Capture the Moment</strong><br>Save screenshots of your favorite characters and outfits. Share your creations with friends or use them as inspiration for your next design.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/Ball_02.gif?t=1725550327\" /><br><br>\u2702\ufe0f<strong>Paper Dolls</strong><br>Bring your digital creations to life by printing out your characters as adorable &quot;paper dolls\u201d. Print in color or color the outfits yourself!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/doll_03.gif?t=1725550327\" /><br><br>\ud83d\udc57<strong>Build Your Wardrobe</strong><br>Create freely and save your favorite outfits for later use. Switch easily between different creations and expand your wardrobe! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/Wardrobe_02.gif?t=1725550327\" /><br><br>\ud83e\uddf5<strong>Casual and Relaxing</strong><br>This game is designed for those seeking a relaxing experience while also learning a thing or two about historical fashion. Or for all the fashion enthusiasts out there just wanting to dive into the details of 1820s fashion. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/Casual.gif?t=1725550327\" /><br><br>Unleash your inner tailor and relive the grace and style of past fashions. Whether you're a history enthusiast or simply love the art of fashion, this is where you can create, explore, and appreciate historical fashion!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Color Enthusiast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2692430/4c03db5fa526aeb6da599c53d4ba2f3cf38acf3e.jpg"},{"name":"Passion For Fashion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2692430/256dcf8c47674464f00131fce84a30e8b9886ab1.jpg"},{"name":"Beauty Takes Time","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2692430/8e037500fd3cd61329793febc585c522cd900239.jpg"},{"name":"I Love Paper Dolls!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2692430/ce4545e58ca6a48f7ae69e4d75701c4458395b80.jpg"},{"name":"History Lover","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2692430/9835a5469a344d86ae6eac19f127ede35150ad7e.jpg"},{"name":"Pretty Patterns","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2692430/1a6a4bbb07300b28fd279dc6a2d50872e5c79e5c.jpg"},{"name":"Attention to Detail","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/